module REQ_ADMIN_HIST_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-ADMIN-HIST-01
 * Title       : Admin Transaction History View
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
